.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-MEMPOOL" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-mempool \- list unconfirmed on-chain transactions
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-mempool
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns unconfirmed on-chain transactions known to the Core Lightning
daemon via
.BR listtransactions .
.PP
Output:
.nf
[{txid, amount_sat, type}]
.fi
Returns an empty array when the daemon is not reachable or there are
no pending transactions.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-funds (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
